Command line tool for the UVa Online Judge website

Building
========
- git clone http://github.com/lucastan/libjava.git 
- Follow the instructions to install ANT and to build libjava-1.0.0.jar 
- Copy libjava-1.0.0.jar to the lib dir
- Build this by typing "ant"
- You will get dist-1.0.0/uva-cli-1.0.0-all.jar

Usage
=====


This is still incomplete yet.
Hopefully it will be done over the next few days when I'm free.

Features:
- Submit a file to the OJ through command line
- See your submissions
- See your statistics
- Password-less submissions

More features coming soon:
- Auto-retry submitting the solution (when UVA is down)
- Connects to UVAtoolkit
- Get statistics on a problem

Implementation:
Source code is included so you know there is no virus in it !

Please let me know if there is any problem!

